<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07887</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT CREATING THE PHILIPPINE CANCER CENTER, PROVIDING FUNDS THEREFOR AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to create and establish a specialized cancer center known as “Philippine Cancer Center” that shall promote and engage in scientific research for the prevention of cancer and the care and/or treatment of cancer patients; facilitate and encourage the exchange of ideas and information on the prevention, treatment and control of cancer; and develop public interest on cancer awareness and general health.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “Philippine Cancer Center Act of 2018.”</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>VARGAS, ALFRED D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-06-27</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Del Mar (000 2018-08-06)</td><td>2. Sangcopan (000 2018-10-10)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON GOVERNMENT REORGANIZATION ON 2018-07-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SECONDARILY REFERRED TO THE COMMITTEE(S) ON HEALTH</td></tr></table>